Label: AdministrativeArea
Description: A geographical region under the jurisdiction of a particular government.

Label: Audience
Description: Intended audience for an item, i.e. the group for whom the item was created.

Label: CategoryCode
Description: A category code from a controlled vocabulary or taxonomy.

Label: ContactPoint
Description: A contact point for a person or organization.

Label: OpeningHoursSpecification
Description: A structured value providing information about the opening hours of a place or service.

Label: Organization
Description: An organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.

Label: Place
Description: Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.

Label: Service
Description: A service provided by an organization or individual.

Label: ServiceChannel
Description: A means for accessing a service, e.g. a phone number, website, or physical location.

Label: TextObject
Description: A text file, including articles, speeches, presentations, etc.

Label: WebPage
Description: A web page, typically from a website.

Label: Activity
Description: An activity is something that occurs over a period of time and acts upon or with entities; it may include consuming, processing, transforming, modifying, relocating, using, or generating entities.

Label: Collection
Description: A collection is an Entity that provides a structure (e.g. set, list, etc.) to some constituents (which are themselves Entities).

Label: Entity
Description: An entity is a physical, digital, conceptual, or other kind of thing with some fixed aspects; entities may be real or imaginary.

Label: address
Description: Physical address of the item.

Label: areaServed
Description: The geographic area where a service or offered item is provided.

Label: audienceType
Description: The target group associated with a given audience (e.g., veterans, car owners, musicians).

Label: availableChannel
Description: A means of accessing the service (e.g. a phone bank, a web site, a location).

Label: category
Description: A category for the item.

Label: closes
Description: The closing hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.

Label: codeValue
Description: A short textual code that uniquely identifies the value.

Label: conditionsOfAccess
Description: Conditions that affect the availability of, or method(s) of access to, an item.

Label: containedInPlace
Description: The basic containment relation between a place and one that contains it.

Label: dayOfWeek
Description: The day of the week for which these opening hours are valid.

Label: description
Description: A description of the item.

Label: disambiguatingDescription
Description: A sub property of description providing a short description to disambiguate instances with similar names.

Label: hasMap
Description: A URL to a map of the place.

Label: hoursAvailable
Description: The hours during which this service or contact is available.

Label: identifier
Description: The identifier property represents any kind of identifier for any kind of Thing.

Label: inCodeSet
Description: A CategoryCodeSet that contains this category code.

Label: latitude
Description: The latitude of a location.

Label: longitude
Description: The longitude of a location.

Label: name
Description: The name of the item.

Label: opens
Description: The opening hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.

Label: provider
Description: The service provider, service operator, or service performer.

Label: sameAs
Description: URL of a reference Web page that unambiguously indicates the item's identity.

Label: serviceLocation
Description: The location where the service is provided.

Label: servicePhone
Description: The phone number to use to access the service.

Label: serviceUrl
Description: The website to access the service.

Label: telephone
Description: The telephone number.

Label: text
Description: The textual content of this CreativeWork.

Label: type
Description: The subject is an instance of a class.

Label: generated
Description: An activity generated an entity.

Label: hadMember
Description: A collection had a member (entity).

Label: influenced
Description: This is the inverse of wasInfluencedBy, and can be used to refer to the object of an influence.

Label: wasDerivedFrom
Description: A derivation is a transformation of an entity into another, an update of an entity resulting in a new one, or the construction of a new entity based on a pre-existing entity.

Label: wasGeneratedBy
Description: Generation is the completion of production of a new entity by an activity. This entity did not exist before generation and becomes available for usage after this generation.

Label: wasInfluencedBy
Description: An entity, activity, or agent was influenced by another entity, activity, or agent. Influence is the capacity of an entity, activity, or agent to have an effect on the character, development, or behavior of another.
